---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import DefaultCard from "../components/DefaultCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Vaimiti DOCK | Design Portfolio">
  <main class="size-full">
    {/* Hero section */}
    <div
      class="flex w-full flex-col border-b-2 border-dotted px-4 py-40 md:px-4 xl:mr-40 xl:px-6 2xl:mr-64"
    >
      <div
        class="flex w-full flex-col px-1 md:px-4 lg:w-9/12 lg:place-self-end lg:px-8 2xl:w-2/3"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline pr-8">
            <p class="pr-1 text-6xl font-medium">Hell</p>
            <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="logo" height="36" width="36" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
            <p class="pr-2 text-6xl font-medium">w</p>
            <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="logo" height="36" width="36" />
            <p class="pl-1 text-6xl font-medium">rld</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="xl:pr-40">
          <p class="pt-10 text-sm">
            I’m Vai, a Product Designer exploring South East Asia.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-4 text-sm">
            Through work experience and side projects I’ve experimented with a variety of
            disciplines from UX research, product design and project management,
            to web design and branding. <br /> From my previous experience at <a href="https://shadow.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:font-medium underline">Shadow</a>,
            I really enjoyed designing while taking the lead on a project. I'm now
            interesting in learning some code to better understand the technical
            constraints behind designs.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-4 text-sm">
            I can’t tell you that I'm active on social media but I will try, soon or
            later. <br /> You can still find me on <a href="https://x.com/DockVaimiti" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:font-medium underline">Twitter</a>, or you can contact me to
            <a href="mailto:hello@vaimitidock.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:font-medium underline">hello@vaimitidock.com</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="pt-4 text-sm">
            I’m currently crafting designs for <a href="https://filament.sh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:font-medium underline">Filament</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Section 1 */}

    <div
      class="flex flex-col border-b-2 border-dotted px-4 py-40 md:flex-row md:space-x-6 md:px-8"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-none pb-8 md:w-3/12 md:pb-0 2xl:w-1/3">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
          <p class="pr-2 text-base font-medium">Selected</p>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
            <p class="pr-0.5 text-base font-medium">w</p>
            <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="logo" height="10" width="10" />
            <p class="pl-0.5 text-base font-medium">rks</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:space-y-16">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-flow-row lg:grid-cols-6 lg:gap-4"
        >
          <a
            href="/projects/ichiba"
            class="flex w-full pb-16 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-span-1 lg:pb-0"
          >
            <DefaultCard
              mediaType="image"
              mediaSrc="/assets/covers/ichiba-thumbnail.jpg"
              title="Ichiba Market"
              style="w-auto hover:opacity-95"
              justify="start"
              showDescription={true}
              description1="Web Design"
              description2="2024"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="/projects/onix"
            class="w-3/6 pb-16 lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-5 lg:row-span-2 lg:w-full lg:pb-0"
          >
            <DefaultCard
              mediaType="image"
              mediaSrc="/assets/covers/onix-thumbnail.jpg"
              title="Onix Wallet Extension"
              style="w-auto hover:opacity-95"
              justify="start"
              showDescription={true}
              description1="UX/UI Design"
              description2="2023"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-flow-row lg:grid-cols-6 lg:gap-4"
        >
          <a
            href="/projects/shadow-wallet"
            class="w-3/6 pb-16 lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-span-2 lg:w-full lg:pb-0"
          >
            <DefaultCard
              mediaType="image"
              mediaSrc="/assets/covers/shadow-wallet-thumbnail.jpg"
              title="Shadow Wallet Extension"
              style="w-auto hover:opacity-90"
              justify="start"
              showDescription={true}
              description1="UX/UI Design"
              description2="2022-2023"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="/projects/shadow-exchange"
            class="flex w-full lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-span-1 lg:pb-0"
          >
            <DefaultCard
              mediaType="image"
              mediaSrc="/assets/covers/shadow-exchange-thumbnail.jpg"
              title="Shadow NFT Exchange"
              style="w-auto hover:opacity-90"
              justify="start"
              showDescription={true}
              description1="UX/UI Design"
              description2="2021-2023"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Section 2 */}
    <div
      class="flex flex-col border-b-2 border-dotted px-4 py-40 md:flex-row md:space-x-6 md:px-8"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-none pb-8 md:w-3/12 md:pb-0 2xl:w-1/3">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
          <p class="pr-2 text-base font-medium">Side</p>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
            <p class="pr-0.5 text-base font-medium">pr</p>
            <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="logo" height="10" width="10" />
            <p class="text-base font-medium">jects</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:grid lg:grid-flow-row lg:grid-cols-6 lg:gap-4 xl:w-2/3"
      >
        <a
          href=""
          class="flex w-full pb-16 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-span-1 lg:pb-0"
        >
          <DefaultCard
            mediaType="image"
            mediaSrc="/assets/covers/boc-thumbnail.jpg"
            title="Build onchain"
            width="w-auto"
            justify="start"
            showDescription={true}
            description1="UX/UI Design"
            description2="2024"
          />
        </a>
        <a
          href=""
          class="w-3/6 lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-5 lg:row-span-2 lg:w-full lg:pb-0"
        >
          <DefaultCard
            mediaType="image"
            mediaSrc="/assets/covers/gimmy-thumbnail.jpg"
            title="Gimmy Mobile App"
            width="w-auto"
            justify="start"
            showDescription={true}
            description1="UX/UI Design"
            description2="2024"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    {/* Section 3 */}
    <div
      class="flex w-full flex-col border-b-2 border-dotted px-4 py-40 md:flex-row md:px-8"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-none pb-8 md:w-3/12 md:pb-0 2xl:w-1/3">
        <div class="col-span-2 col-start-1 row-span-1">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
            <p class="pr-2 text-base font-medium">Site</p>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-baseline">
              <p class="pr-0.5 text-base font-medium">inf</p>
              <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="logo" height="10" width="10" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex text-sm md:w-9/12">
        <p>
          This is the first website I build from scratch after learning some js
          and React. <br />
          <br /> This site is built with Astro and is hosted on Vercel, you can view
          the code source here. I used Tailwind CSS framework and the font is Spline
          Sans Mono only.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    width: 100%;
  }
</style>
